# Paytm Logo

## On Dark Backgrounds
Used on: `bg-[#004299]`, overlays, branded headers (login, authorization).
- All SVG paths: `fill="white"` — entirely white, no accent colors
- Position: top-left of container
- Size: `w-[100px] h-[34px]`
- Wrapper: `relative shrink-0`

## Component
- `PaytmLogoWhite` at `src/app/components/PaytmLogoWhite.tsx`
- SVG `preserveAspectRatio` set for proper alignment
